title: TORE UP

description.plain:
“TORE UP” embraces a less-explored side of Don Toliver’s music, being centered around a bass-heavy instrumental and paired with a prevalent guitar riff sampled from She Died Real Pretty. Don lyrically highlights his fast life, open to drug use and sex, as he actively pursues a new aesthetic for his fourth studio album, HARDSTONE PSYCHO.

The track was debuted at his 2024 Rolling Loud California set on March 17, 2024 alongside a live guitar player. Additionally, Don affirmed HARDSTONE PSYCHO’s summer 2024 release after performing.
